  "texts": [
    "Moreover, they assist students with administrative tasks such as grade inquiries, course enrollment, and examination schedules, thereby reducing their burden.",
    "• In customer support and service: In customer support and service, businesses are leveraging chatbots to enhance customer satisfaction and stay competitive in a rapidly evolving technological market.",
    "One of the key advantages of chatbots is their round-the-clock availability, which ensures that customers always have a resource to turn to for their queries.",
    "These support chatbots can answer the most frequently asked questions (FAQ) [46] in real time, guide customers in selecting the best product based on their preferences [47], or provide initial engagement with the company before escalating unresolved issues.",
    "This constant support helps customers feel valued and well-cared for, even when they encounter issues or have inquiries to submit [48]."
  ]
}